Below is a pandas template pack you can use to compare iteration 1 vs iteration 2 from simple checks through more advanced analysis.

I’m assuming you have something like:
	•	acct_id
	•	score_date
	•	xgb_score
	•	maybe sar_label
	•	maybe sar_type
	•	maybe suspicious window columns later

I’ll keep it modular so you can copy pieces as needed.

